the world of princess sorrow
-dark.
-particles floating around.
-glowing people.
-strange ambient noises.
-distant music that plays on a high piano.
-people will stay in specific villages. some will travel throughout the land.
-some buildings will be too scary for npc characters to enter so only the main character can.
-you can clear out the horrors of the buildings as a side quest and it will be a new building such as a shop or blacksmith.
-if you want you can take one of the spooky housing for your own.